<p><b>What is consumer behavior in marketing Philip Kotler?</b> 4.1 Philip Kotler's model of consumer behavior Consumers' shopping behavior will be done in 5 steps: Knowing the needs, searching for information, comparing between products, making a purchase, evaluating products. Accordingly, the Philip Kotler model is also built based on these 5 steps.</p>
<p><b>What is the model of buying behavior by Philip Kotler?</b> Five stages make up the model: need identification, information search, alternative evaluation, buy decision, and post-purchase evaluation.</p>
